    public class PluginSelector
extends javax.swing.JDialog
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.event.MouseListener, javax.swing.event.ListSelectionListener, java.awt.event.WindowListener
    Represents a plugin selector. A simple dialog to pick the name of a plugin. The dialog filters already loaded plugins from the list of plugins.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.8 $
